{"pageProps":{"post":{"title":"信号処理入門１","date":"2021-08-12T20:35:07","slug":"信号処理入門1","content":"<h2>信号処理とは？</h2>\n<h3>どんな処理か？</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>フィルタ処理\n<ul>\n<li>特定周波数成分を取り出す</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>フーリエ変換\n<ul>\n<li>周波数帯域で分ける</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>実用例</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>音声信号からのノイズ除去\n<ul>\n<li>スペクトルサブトラクション法\n<ul>\n<li>フーリエ変換 → ノイズ成分を引く</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>画像圧縮\n<ul>\n<li>JPEG\n<ul>\n<li>ブロックにデータを分割し、離散コサイン変換（直交変換）する</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>デジタル信号</h2>\n<h3>アナログ信号を取り込む</h3>\n<p>デジタル信号に変換するため、\n一定時間間隔でサンプリング（標本化）する必要がある。</p>\n<p>また、取りうる範囲を決めておき、値を最も近いレベルの値に変換する量子化を行うことで\n信号値が離散化される。</p>\n<h2>周期信号</h2>\n<div><span><span><span>x(t)=Asin⁡(2πTt+ϕ)x(t) = A \\sin (\\frac{2\\pi}{T} t + \\phi)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>x</span><span>(</span><span>t</span><span>)</span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>sin</span><span>(</span><span><span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>T</span></span></span><span><span></span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>2</span><span>π</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span><span>t</span><span></span><span>+</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>ϕ</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>角速度<span><span><span>θ\\theta</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>θ</span></span></span></span></span>, 各周波数<span><span><span>ω\\omega</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>ω</span></span></span></span></span>で時間変化する場合、</p>\n<p>オイラーの公式は</p>\n<div><span><span><span>ejωt=cos⁡ωt+jsin⁡ωte^{j\\omega t} = \\cos \\omega t + j \\sin \\omega t</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span><span>e</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>j</span><span>ω</span><span>t</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>cos</span><span></span><span>ω</span><span>t</span><span></span><span>+</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>j</span><span></span><span>sin</span><span></span><span>ω</span><span>t</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>となる。</p>\n<p>これを <strong>複素正弦波信号</strong> という。</p>\n<p>周期は <span><span><span>T=2π/ωT = 2\\pi/\\omega</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>T</span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>2</span><span>π</span><span>/</span><span>ω</span></span></span></span></span> となる。</p>\n<h2>フーリエ級数</h2>\n<p>角周波数が異なる正弦波を足し合わせると、任意の周期信号を作れる。</p>\n<p>周期<span><span><span>TT</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>T</span></span></span></span></span>の任意の周期信号<span><span><span>x(t)x(t)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>x</span><span>(</span><span>t</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span>は、<span><span><span>ω0=2πT\\omega_0 = \\frac{2\\pi}{T}</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span><span>ω</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>0</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>T</span></span></span></span><span><span></span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span><span>2</span><span>π</span></span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span>（基本角周波数）として</p>\n<div><span><span><span>x(t)=c0+∑k=1∞akcos⁡kω0t+∑k=1∞bksin⁡kω0tx(t) = c_0 + \\sum_{k=1}^\\infty a_k \\cos k\\omega_0 t + \\sum_{k=1}^\\infty b_k \\sin k\\omega_0 t</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>x</span><span>(</span><span>t</span><span>)</span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>c</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>0</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>+</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>k</span><span>=</span><span>1</span></span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>∑</span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>∞</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span><span>a</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>k</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>cos</span><span></span><span>k</span><span><span>ω</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>0</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>t</span><span></span><span>+</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>k</span><span>=</span><span>1</span></span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>∑</span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>∞</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span><span>b</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>k</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>sin</span><span></span><span>k</span><span><span>ω</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>0</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>t</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>と表せる。\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ddaz9etkx/image/upload/v1628832927/202108/1_u7qctu.jpg\" alt=\"image\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ddaz9etkx/image/upload/v1628832932/202108/2_grdrdh.jpg\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h2>複素フーリエ級数</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ddaz9etkx/image/upload/v1628832940/202108/3_weftkx.jpg\" alt=\"image\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ddaz9etkx/image/upload/v1628832946/202108/4_wugojb.jpg\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h3>パーセバルの公式</h3>\n<div><span><span><span>1T∫−T2T2x(t)2dt=σ−∞∞∣ck∣2\\frac{1}{T}\\int_{-\\frac{T}{2}}^{\\frac{T}{2}} x(t)^2 dt = \\sigma_{-\\infty}^\\infty |c_k|^2</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span><span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>T</span></span></span><span><span></span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>1</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span><span></span><span><span>∫</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>−</span><span><span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>2</span></span></span></span><span><span></span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span><span>T</span></span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>2</span></span></span></span><span><span></span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span><span>T</span></span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>x</span><span>(</span><span>t</span><span><span>)</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>d</span><span>t</span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>σ</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>−</span><span>∞</span></span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>∞</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>∣</span><span><span>c</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>k</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span>∣</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>左辺は周期信号<span><span><span>x(t)x(t)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>x</span><span>(</span><span>t</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span> を2乗して1周期区間で平均を取った値であり、平均パワーと呼ぶ。</p>\n<p>平均パワーはその信号の複素フーリエ係数の絶対値の2乗の総和で表せることを示している。</p>\n<h3>まとめ</h3>\n<div><span><span><span>x(t)=∑k=−∞∞ckejkω0tx(t) = \\sum_{k=-\\infty}^\\infty c_k e^{jk\\omega_0t}</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>x</span><span>(</span><span>t</span><span>)</span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>k</span><span>=</span><span>−</span><span>∞</span></span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>∑</span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>∞</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span><span>c</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>k</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span>e</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>j</span><span>k</span><span><span>ω</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>0</span></spa